<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PrimarySourceReference/788> rdfs:label "Primary Source Reference: #788" ;
	a dprr:PrimarySourceReference ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Cic. Verr. II i 153" ;
	dprr:forAssertion <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertion/779> .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/552> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #552" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Victory and triumph over the Volscians (Liv. 6.11-14, and 16.5). Arrested M. Manlius Capitolinus (Liv. 6.15-16; Plut. Cam. 36.4, who names Quintus Capitolinus; cf. Diod. 15.35.3, who places the trial and execution in this year). See Degrassi 101, 391, and on the triumph 539." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/10032> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #10032" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/30> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Triumph de Volsceis. MRR I.101, Itgenshorst p. 263, Rich no. 50." .
